person.persName: Jane Paralee Dycus (Ballard County, Kentucky, resident.)

body.p: Ballard County, Kentucky, resident. Kentucky native. Daughter of Wiley Dycus and Sabre Pickett Dycus. Resident of Ballard County, Kentucky, in 1850. Resident of Ballard County in 1860.
